---
title: Creamy Chipotle Beef Meatballs with Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: Stand back and watch these All-American beef meatballs explode in the pan and shower the dinner table with an array of mouth-watering flavours. Light up your tastebuds with a creamy chipotle mayo to dollop over the meatballs and pan-fried veggies. It’s a celebration you don’t want to miss.
